  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Geisha clan is known for its strong reputation, built on their exceptional beauty, skill in delicate arts, and ability to entertain even the highest lords with their mere presence.</p><p></p><p>At level 3, you gain mastery in Performance and can choose one additional skill based on your Geisha type:</p><ul><li><strong>Dancer:</strong> Choose between Acrobatics, Athletics, Stealth, or Martial Arts.</li><li><strong>Strategic:</strong> Choose between Ninshou, Chakra Control, Perception, or Insight.</li><li><strong>Eloquence:</strong> Choose between Illusions, Deception, Intimidation, or Persuasion.</li></ul><p>You must forsake one of the categories entirely.<br />You will not be able to gain expertise or mastery in any of the skills from that category.<br />You gain an additional rank of mastery in Performance and one more skill from the above list at levels 7, 11, and 15 (Mastery 3 becomes Expertise).<br />As a consequence of your training, you cannot wear or have proficiency in heavy armor under any circumstance.</p>",
